description:
Every ministry will be represented at this year's GC Session, and Family Ministries is no different. ANN Late Nite (ish) chats with Associate Director Elaine Oliver to get the inside look into all the ways Family Ministries will be featured in this year's GC Session. 

#GCSession #Adventist #AdventistChurch
